4. useRef Hook
Definition

useRef is used to access DOM elements directly.

Example
import { useRef } from "react"

function InputFocus(){

 const inputRef = useRef()

 const focusInput = ()=>{
   inputRef.current.focus()
 }

 return(
  <>
   <input ref={inputRef} />
   <button onClick={focusInput}>
     Focus
   </button>
  </>
 )
}
Another Use (Store value without re-render)
const count = useRef(0)
count.current++
